reviews.review_text:
Greatest Hits Set? One has to wonder if the Dead decided to reward the LI crowd for a few great days with this set that reads like a "Greatest Hits" to this point.  The boys are dipping into all eras on this night, and delivering nice, long jams in each one.  This is the GD in prime, early 80's form, and the crowd is just eating it up.  

Wonderful sound for an audience tape of this age.  You can really hear the room and the energy from the crowd.  AUDs like this make me forget the typical Dead SBD show, because you really get a sense of the energy going back and forth between the audience and the band.  Great stuff!
